msgid "records.modeFocus.practice.title"
msgstr "Practice"

msgid "records.modeFocus.practice.description"
msgstr "The core mode for everyday work on speed, accuracy, and weak spots."

msgid "records.modeFocus.practice.recommendation.empty"
msgstr "You need at least one base practice session so the other modes have something solid to stand on."

msgid "records.modeFocus.practice.recommendation.lowAccuracy"
msgstr "Practice is currently slipping in accuracy. It is better to stabilize the base before challenge modes."

msgid "records.modeFocus.practice.recommendation.ready"
msgstr "The base looks solid. Practice can already serve as a warm-up before sprint or flawless survival."

msgid "records.modeFocus.practice.recommendation.building"
msgstr "A few more base sessions and endurance and clean modes will start feeling noticeably steadier."

msgid "records.modeFocus.test.title"
msgstr "Sprint"

msgid "records.modeFocus.test.description"
msgstr "A short timed mode for acceleration, typing density, and error control under time pressure."

msgid "records.modeFocus.test.recommendation.empty"
msgstr "Sprint is not part of the real training cycle yet. One short run is enough to calibrate your pace."

msgid "records.modeFocus.test.recommendation.lowAccuracy"
msgstr "Sprint is losing results to errors. It is useful to keep the pace, but reduce chaotic misses at the start."

msgid "records.modeFocus.test.recommendation.ready"
msgstr "Sprint is already giving a strong speed peak. It can be used as a short control session between practice runs."

msgid "records.modeFocus.test.recommendation.building"
msgstr "The mode is already in play, but it still needs repetition so the pace becomes stable instead of a one-off spike."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.title"
