msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.description"
msgstr "A long run with an error limit and a built-in flawless switch for the stricter version of the mode."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.recommendation.empty"
msgstr "Survival is not part of the rhythm yet. One long run will quickly show whether the skill holds outside short bursts, and the flawless switch can come after the warm-up."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.recommendation.flawlessReady"
msgstr "The internal flawless variant is already giving strong results. The mode can now be used both as a long check and as a precision check via the switch."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.recommendation.lowAccuracy"
msgstr "The mode is limited not by peak speed, but by stability. It is worth improving more even accuracy over long distance, and using the flawless switch only selectively for now."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.recommendation.ready"
msgstr "Survival already looks mature for you. It is a great way to test whether technique breaks down on long text, and the flawless switch can be used as a stricter sub-mode."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.recommendation.building"
msgstr "There is a working base, but the mode still benefits from a few more long runs to smooth out the middle and the end of the text."

msgid "records.modeFocus.survival.recommendation.buildingWithFlawless"
msgstr "There is a working base, but the mode still benefits from a few more long runs to smooth out the middle and the end of the text and make the flawless switch more reliable."

