msgstr "A small word pool shows itself best in a compact accuracy-focused mode without a long distance."

msgid "practice.packSummary.reasons.wordsNormalPractice"
msgstr "A medium word pool works best as a universal regular practice."

msgid "practice.packSummary.reasons.mixedTightPractice"
msgstr "A short mixed pool should not be stretched into harsh or long scenarios; it needs a calmer mid-distance run."

msgid "practice.packSummary.reasons.mixedLongSurvival"
msgstr "Mixed content with longer fragments opens up better in a long steady run."

msgid "practice.packSummary.reasons.mixedNormalPractice"
msgstr "A mixed pack without a strong bias fits best in normal practice."

