msgstr "The import stays at a medium distance first, so the pack can be checked in a base mode before moving into a long survival run."

msgid "practice.importPreset.reasons.rhythmAfterStrict"
msgstr "For the first start, the pack is shortened into a calm short practice so the user is not overloaded with a harsh scenario right after import."

msgid "practice.importPreset.reasons.normalStable"
msgstr "The pack already looks stable enough for standard practice, so an extra short preset is not needed."

